@c This file contains the entry for the --ctf option that is common
@c to both readelf and objdump.

@item --ctf[=@var{section}]
@cindex CTF
@cindex Compact Type Format

Display the contents of the specified CTF or BTF section.  CTF sections
themselves contain many subsections, all of which are displayed in order.

By default, display the name of the section named @var{.ctf}, which is the
name emitted by @command{ld}.
